{
  "id": "2021-08-25_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-08-25",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "드림빌더 (Dreambuilders)",
  "duration_sec": 686.92,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-08-25_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.56,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.56,
      "end": 3.66,
      "text": "8월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.66,
      "end": 6.96,
      "text": "A Fantasy World, A World of Illusion으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.96,
      "end": 8.1,
      "text": "여러분을 초대하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 8.1,
      "end": 10.06,
      "text": "Dream Builder"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.06,
      "end": 11.16,
      "text": "잘 오셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.04,
      "end": 14.16,
      "text": "조크쌤, 크리스쌤"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.16,
      "end": 16.72,
      "text": "Yes, you are 조쌤, I am 크쌤"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.72,
      "end": 18.82,
      "text": "Together we are 조크쌤"
    },
    {
      "start": 18.82,
      "end": 20.92,
      "text": "와우, 너무 쿵짝이 짝짝 맞죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.62,
      "end": 24.22,
      "text": "우리 어저께 미나가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.22,
      "end": 26.4,
      "text": "She had a strong will to find Jenny"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.4,
      "end": 28.4,
      "text": "She really feels guilty"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.4,
      "end": 31.54,
      "text": "Yeah, but Jenny was still in a dream trash"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.54,
      "end": 32.62,
      "text": "Dream dumpster"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.62,
      "end": 32.94,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.94,
      "end": 35.06,
      "text": "Full of old unwanted dreams"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.06,
      "end": 37.38,
      "text": "와, 그래서 과연 이 꿈속에"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.38,
      "end": 39.44,
      "text": "Jenny가 영원히 갇혀버릴지"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.44,
      "end": 41.52,
      "text": "걱정이 되는 상황인데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.52,
      "end": 43.9,
      "text": "Back at home, she's still on her bed"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.9,
      "end": 44.78,
      "text": "Asleep"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.78,
      "end": 46.82,
      "text": "As if she were in a coma"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.82,
      "end": 47.3,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.3,
      "end": 48.48,
      "text": "The doctor comes"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.48,
      "end": 49.74,
      "text": "Her mom comes"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.74,
      "end": 51.34,
      "text": "They're so worried about her"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.34,
      "end": 51.92,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.92,
      "end": 53.5,
      "text": "현실 세계에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.5,
      "end": 55.06,
      "text": "Jenny가 그저 침대에 누워서"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.06,
      "end": 56.28,
      "text": "눈을 탁 감고"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.28,
      "end": 59.12,
      "text": "코마 상태에 있는 것 같아 보였단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.12,
      "end": 60.38,
      "text": "얼마나 온 가족들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.38,
      "end": 61.48,
      "text": "걱정을 했나 몰라요"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.48,
      "end": 62.2,
      "text": "걱정 많아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.2,
      "end": 72.8,
      "text": "Yeah, so if you're in the dream world"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.8,
      "end": 75.38,
      "text": "Too long, you get stuck there"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.38,
      "end": 78.0,
      "text": "And you can never go back to reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.0,
      "end": 80.54,
      "text": "너무 걱정이 되는 상황이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.54,
      "end": 81.42,
      "text": "Yeah, it's funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.42,
      "end": 85.5,
      "text": "Sometimes the line between a dream and reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.5,
      "end": 87.3,
      "text": "It's a very fine line"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.3,
      "end": 88.72,
      "text": "Is this a dream?"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.9,
      "end": 89.9,
      "text": "Is this reality?"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.14,
      "end": 91.8,
      "text": "I can't tell the difference"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.8,
      "end": 93.46,
      "text": "지금 이거 혹시 꿈은 아니죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.52,
      "end": 94.7,
      "text": "그럴 때가 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.7,
      "end": 96.32,
      "text": "지금 꿈을 수도 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.32,
      "end": 98.32,
      "text": "Oh, what if it's a dream?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.34,
      "end": 100.62,
      "text": "What if I'm just dreaming?"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.86,
      "end": 101.2,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.2,
      "end": 102.34,
      "text": "Who am I? Where am I?"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.48,
      "end": 104.32,
      "text": "꿈에 관련된 이야기 중에 혹시"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.32,
      "end": 106.22,
      "text": "Have you ever heard of 호잡 지몽?"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.66,
      "end": 107.5,
      "text": "I have"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.5,
      "end": 108.22,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.22,
      "end": 109.02,
      "text": "네, 사자성어"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.02,
      "end": 110.52,
      "text": "네, 혹시 의미도 아세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.72,
      "end": 111.5,
      "text": "The butterfly"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.5,
      "end": 111.88,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.88,
      "end": 113.6,
      "text": "It's about a butterfly"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.6,
      "end": 114.78,
      "text": "Someone who dreams"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.78,
      "end": 116.68,
      "text": "Was it like 장자?"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.9,
      "end": 119.38,
      "text": "It was from China or something"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.38,
      "end": 120.14,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.14,
      "end": 121.66,
      "text": "He dreams he's a butterfly"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.66,
      "end": 122.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.32,
      "end": 123.04,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.04,
      "end": 125.32,
      "text": "And then he thinks about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.32,
      "end": 125.66,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.66,
      "end": 128.18,
      "text": "Is the butterfly dreaming that he's me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.18,
      "end": 130.64,
      "text": "Or am I dreaming that I'm the butterfly?"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.84,
      "end": 132.1,
      "text": "What is reality?"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.28,
      "end": 133.38,
      "text": "What is this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.6,
      "end": 136.4,
      "text": "와, 이렇게 디테일한 내용까지 다 알고 계시다니"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.4,
      "end": 136.62,
      "text": "진짜"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.62,
      "end": 138.26,
      "text": "You have plenty of common sense"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.26,
      "end": 139.88,
      "text": "Is that common sense?"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.92,
      "end": 141.56,
      "text": "Yeah, 진짜 대단합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.56,
      "end": 145.08,
      "text": "어쨌든 이 호잡 지몽이라는 말은"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.08,
      "end": 149.98,
      "text": "이 무라일체 혹은 인생무상에 관련된 꿈이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.98,
      "end": 151.22,
      "text": "꿈에 대한 이야기잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.22,
      "end": 153.64,
      "text": "So, it's about the vanity of life"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.64,
      "end": 155.4,
      "text": "이렇게도 표현할 수 있을 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.4,
      "end": 156.16,
      "text": "The vanity"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.16,
      "end": 156.6,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.6,
      "end": 157.64,
      "text": "The vanity"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.64,
      "end": 160.62,
      "text": "아, 참 묵직한 메시지가 되겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.62,
      "end": 165.54,
      "text": "과연 우리 미나가 제니를 꿈속에서 잘 구할 수 있을지 상상하시면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.54,
      "end": 168.01,
      "text": "오늘 내용 먼저 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.01,
      "end": 168.51,
      "text": "Please"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.51,
      "end": 170.71,
      "text": "Just let me wake up from this nightmare"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.71,
      "end": 173.06,
      "text": "That's why I'm here"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.06,
      "end": 173.72,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.72,
      "end": 175.7,
      "text": "You've been gone too long"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.7,
      "end": 176.22,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.64,
      "end": 179.16,
      "text": "We need to get you back to your stage before it's too late"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.16,
      "end": 179.9,
      "text": "But why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.14,
      "end": 181.2,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.28,
      "end": 181.48,
      "text": "Um"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.48,
      "end": 182.56,
      "text": "What happens then?"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.9,
      "end": 183.14,
      "text": "Well"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.14,
      "end": 185.62,
      "text": "What is this place?"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.16,
      "end": 186.82,
      "text": "Oh, Jenny"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.82,
      "end": 188.1,
      "text": "I'm so sorry"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.1,
      "end": 190.46,
      "text": "Don't touch me"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.46,
      "end": 191.16,
      "text": "I"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.16,
      "end": 191.72,
      "text": "It's fine"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.72,
      "end": 193.86,
      "text": "Just show me how I get out of this place"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.86,
      "end": 195.9,
      "text": "We need to get to that tower"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.9,
      "end": 198.12,
      "text": "We'll get you back home, Jenny"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.12,
      "end": 199.8,
      "text": "Oh, no"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.8,
      "end": 201.58,
      "text": "It's destroyed"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.58,
      "end": 204.62,
      "text": "Oh, 그나마 다행이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.62,
      "end": 206.14,
      "text": "Jenny의 목소리가 들렸잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.14,
      "end": 206.94,
      "text": "She's here"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.94,
      "end": 210.1,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean I found Jenny with cell phone"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.1,
      "end": 211.06,
      "text": "Ring, ring"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.06,
      "end": 212.0,
      "text": "기억나시죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.12,
      "end": 212.56,
      "text": "Where are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.62,
      "end": 213.04,
      "text": "Where are you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.16,
      "end": 214.12,
      "text": "되게 재밌는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.12,
      "end": 218.26,
      "text": "Jenny가 그런 꿈속에도 휴대폰을 갖고 갔다라는 설정인 거잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.26,
      "end": 219.36,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.36,
      "end": 220.54,
      "text": "Cell phone은 역시"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.54,
      "end": 222.42,
      "text": "Are a crucial necessity"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.42,
      "end": 223.78,
      "text": "Even in your dreams"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.78,
      "end": 224.14,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.14,
      "end": 225.64,
      "text": "Always have your cell phone"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.64,
      "end": 229.62,
      "text": "저는 꿈속에서 휴대폰을 사용하는 꿈은 꿔본 적이 없는 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.62,
      "end": 232.1,
      "text": "I try to keep my cell phone away from the bed"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.1,
      "end": 232.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.42,
      "end": 233.28,
      "text": "I tried"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.28,
      "end": 234.02,
      "text": "그래야 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.02,
      "end": 235.24,
      "text": "It didn't work though"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.24,
      "end": 237.42,
      "text": "I keep looking at it"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.42,
      "end": 237.6,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.6,
      "end": 238.34,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.34,
      "end": 240.7,
      "text": "Oh, 그럼 deep sleep을 좀 방해할 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.7,
      "end": 241.96,
      "text": "I think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.96,
      "end": 242.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.28,
      "end": 242.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.74,
      "end": 245.2,
      "text": "점점 더 멀리 멀리 멀리"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.2,
      "end": 247.88,
      "text": "옆방에다가 한번 두고 주무시는 건 어떨지"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.88,
      "end": 249.58,
      "text": "And then when my alarm goes off"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.58,
      "end": 250.92,
      "text": "I have to get up"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.92,
      "end": 251.44,
      "text": "어머나"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.44,
      "end": 252.14,
      "text": "Right away"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.14,
      "end": 253.42,
      "text": "아, 네, 취소할게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.42,
      "end": 256.14,
      "text": "No, it's a good incentive to get up"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.14,
      "end": 256.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.42,
      "end": 258.7,
      "text": "Because the alarm will wake up the whole family"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.7,
      "end": 260.9,
      "text": "So, 나쁜 생각 안 했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.9,
      "end": 261.74,
      "text": "Oh, 네네"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.74,
      "end": 262.58,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.58,
      "end": 263.2,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.2,
      "end": 264.02,
      "text": "You try it first"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.02,
      "end": 265.2,
      "text": "저요? 저"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.2,
      "end": 266.42,
      "text": "아, 알겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.42,
      "end": 268.56,
      "text": "오늘 밤에 한번 해보도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.56,
      "end": 269.78,
      "text": "Let me know how it goes"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.78,
      "end": 270.32,
      "text": "Yeah, 알겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.32,
      "end": 271.26,
      "text": "And then I'll decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.26,
      "end": 271.8,
      "text": "All right"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.8,
      "end": 272.8,
      "text": "I'll tell you"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.8,
      "end": 273.8,
      "text": "Thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.8,
      "end": 275.42,
      "text": "네, 표현들 먼저 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.26,
      "end": 278.52,
      "text": "Let me wake up from this nightmare"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.52,
      "end": 282.1,
      "text": "Let me wake up from this nightmare"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.1,
      "end": 284.52,
      "text": "뭔가 좀 리드미컬하게 읽어봤습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.52,
      "end": 286.24,
      "text": "Let me wake up from this nightmare"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.24,
      "end": 288.5,
      "text": "이 nightmare 무슨 의미일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.66,
      "end": 289.68,
      "text": "악몽이 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.68,
